     )
Description: 
    Methods from Yeh, Rice, and Dubin (2022, doi:10.1080/00031305.2021.1967781;
    arXiv:2010.00781) for comparing two continuously updated probabilistic
    forecasts under squared (Brier) loss: pointwise loss and variance, a global
    delta test (Monte Carlo p-values), simulation designs, and a naive
    pointwise band plot.
